title: PSN Stuff - Download 4000 PSN Games + DLC. EASY ACTIVATION!
description:
Latest Version of PSN Stuff (1.83). New database with over 4000 PSN Games and DLC. Latest additions at bottom of list.

Very easy to use. Download .PKG and .RAP. 

Run PSN Patch on PS3 to activate content, much easier than ReactPSN, no need to make any accounts, just run PSN Patch and press L1 to install all .rap and .edat files on USB drive (in exdata folder).

That's it! Give it a try, you will be amazed how quick and easy it is to use.

Like a free PSN store 8)

Enjoy!
